p-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">艺电</a>透露，下一款<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/battlefield"><em>《战地》</em></a>游戏将是该系列的“重新想象”，并具有“真正互联的生态系统”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/features/gaming-features/sony-says-battlefield-is-outmatched-by-call-of-duty-is-that-true-3356043">索尼称《战地》胜过《使命召唤》——这是真的吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一消息源于艺电<a href="https://keytogaming.com/2023/08/02/electronic-arts-ea-earnings-call-transcript-q1-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">最近召开的 2024 财年第一季度财报电话会议</a>，首席执行官安德鲁·威尔逊 (Andrew Wilson) 介绍了该发行商即将推出的游戏。</p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dragon-age-dreadwolf">《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/project-rene">《雷内计划》</a></em> （或更通俗地称为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-sims-5-release-date-plot-news-rumours-and-more-2973889"><em>《模拟人生 5</em></a> 》）、新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ea-begins-production-on-single-player-iron-man-game-3394633"><em>《钢铁侠》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ea-reveals-black-panther-single-player-action-game-3466990"><em>《黑豹》</em></a>游戏，以及下一款<em>《战地》</em>都是艺电将如何“打造无与伦比的 IP 驱动平台，娱乐大规模在线社区、讲述轰动的故事，并放大社区的力量。”</p><p>关于“重新构想的”<em>战地</em>体验中“真正互联的生态系统”是什么样子的细节很少。但是， <em>《战地 2042》</em>在 2021 年推出时的灾难性发布肯定是开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ea-dice">DICE</a>和艺电下次都会尽力避免的事情。 </p><figure id="attachment_3477082" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477082" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3477082" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/battlefield-2042-next-game-will-be-reimagination-of-the-games-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3477082" class="wp-caption-text"> 《战地 2042》 图片来源：Electronic Arts</figcaption></figure><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/battlefield-2042-review-3092844"><em>《NME</em> 》对<em>《战地 2042》</em>的三星级评论</a>中，这款游戏被描述为“令人惊叹”、“过于复杂”和“精心设计，尽可能地令人困惑”。不过，在 DICE 团队的努力下，游戏的情况出现了转机。</p><p> “没有人能像<em>《战地 2042》</em>那样进行大规模战斗，”Jake Tucker 在<em>NME</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/battlefield-2042-has-completed-its-redemption-arc-3399677">对该游戏发布一年后的最新评论</a>中说道。 “感觉这款游戏有点脱离了自己的方式，让人们陷入困境并享受<em>《战地》</em>一直以来闻名的激烈交火。”</p><p>游戏的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/battlefield-2042-gets-hourglass-rework-and-squad-orders-in-update-5-2-0-3475575">最新补丁</a>增加了小队命令，以及确保小队协同工作的能力，对沙漏进行了重大修改，并为拱形武器添加了全面战争附件。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-composer-yuka-kitamura-leaves-fromsoftware-3477026">北村由香 (Yuka Kitamura) 宣布退出</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a> ，此前她为 FromSoftware 创作了一系列最著名的配乐 10 年。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/next-battlefield-game-will-be-a-reimagination-of-the-series-3477056">下一款“战地”游戏将是该系列的“重新想象”，该系列</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
