场景》首次在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jessica-chastain-oscar-isaac-friendship-never-quite-been-the-same-scenes-from-a-marriage-3477028">后，奥斯卡·伊萨克 (Oscar Isaac) 的友谊“从未完全一样”</a> 。</p> ;
